## Welcome to **Q**uery**B**erg
**Q**uery**B**erg is a jQuery Plugin enabling you to search the items on [Project Gutenberg](http://www.gutenberg.org/)

### CODE
```
$.qb('goethe', function(data) {
	$.each(data.items, function(index, item){
		// here comes each items matching with 'goethe'...
	});
});
```

### DEMO
Here is a live [DEMO PAGE](http://blog.turutosiya.com/demo/queryberg/index.html).
